-- Schneider in talks with Carlyle, PAI to sell sensors unit
-- By James Regan
-- Thu Apr 03, 2014 11:56AM EDT
-- None



PARIS, April 3 (Reuters) - French electrical gear maker Schneider Electric <SCHN.PA> said it was in exclusive talks with The Carlyle Group and PAI Partners to sell its sensors unit in a deal based on an enterprise value of $900 million.

